t catch. F001: 21 code-webflow references had `### Purpose` copied verbatim from the H1 intro, violating the create-skill template's explicit non-duplication rule — each Purpose was rewritten to a section-derived, intro-distinct statement (0 duplicates across all 163). F002: the completion claim overstated \"0 broken links hub-wide\"; a fenced-code-aware scan found two pre-existing non-navigational artifacts (an illustrative `005-example.com` example path and a filename quoted in changelog prose, both authored by prior commits) — the claim was narrowed to its true renamed-file scope rather than editing correct documentation.\n <!-- /ANCHOR:decisions -->\n \n ---\n","metadata":{"output":"babefb0586 fix(sk-code): remediate 019 deep-review P1s — Purpose de-dup + link-claim scope\n .../animation_workflows/motion_dev_advanced.md     |   2 +-\n .../motion_dev_and_performance.md                  |   2 +-\n .../testing_and_common_issues.md                   |   2 +-\n .../raf_ric_microtask_and_posttask.md              |   2 +-\n .../async_patterns/timing_compat_and_webflow.md    |   2 +-\n .../restoration_touch_and_anti_patterns.md         |   2 +-\n .../mime_troubleshooting_and_deployment.md         |   2 +-\n .../state_machine_worker_and_forms.md              |   2 +-\n .../condition_based_waiting.md                     |   3 +-\n .../validation_minification_and_cdn.md             |   2 +-\n .../resize_best_practices_and_shared.md            |   2 +-\n .../budgets_and_anti_patterns.md                   |   2 +-\n .../owasp_prototype_and_safe_access.md             |   2 +-\n .../autoplay_accessibility_and_naming.md           |   2 +-\n .../initialization_and_troubleshooting.md          |   2 +-\n .../best_practices_and_summary.md                  |   2 +-\n .../botpoison_and_finsweet.md                      |   2 +-\n .../third_party_integrations/filepond.md           |   2 +-\n .../webflow_patterns/development_and_production.md |   2 +-\n .../finsweet_custom_select_bridge