ion claim overstated \"0 broken links hub-wide\"; a fenced-code-aware scan found two pre-existing non-navigational artifacts (an illustrative `005-example.com` example path and a filename quoted in changelog prose, both authored by prior commits) — the claim was narrowed to its true renamed-file scope rather than editing correct documentation.\n <!-- /ANCHOR:decisions -->\n \n ---\n","exit":0,"truncated":false},"title":"git show --stat --oneline --summary babefb0586 && git diff babefb0586^ babefb0586 -- .opencode/skills/sk-code/code-webflow/references/implementation/third_party_integrations/overview_hls_and_lenis.md .opencode/skills/sk-code/code-webflow/references/css/patterns/tokens_state_machine_and_triggers.md .opencode/skills/sk-code/code-webflow/references/implementation/observer_patterns/mutation_and_intersection.md .opencode/skills/sk-code/code-opencode/references/rust/style_guide/interop_errors_and_parity.md .opencode/specs/sk-code/019-split-doc-template-alignment/implementation-summary.md .opencode/specs/sk-code/019-split-doc-template-alignment/checklist.md","time":{"start":1783915761593,"end":1783915761595}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_0022882c602ad73d016a5464f127fc8191bc376830e0c6be3a"}},"id":"prt_f59aa4f8a001njB0FY8tDVg4Ge","sessionID":"ses_0a65ac46dffebja9CFmlcvrGJ0","messageID":"msg_f59a9e074001szttQ6FV3B4V4D"}}
